<p>It’s nice to see Insomniac return to Spider-Man, if briefly, as the studio is currently preparing its next superhero game, <a href="https://gameinformer.com/state-of-play/2025/09/24/marvels-wolverine-comes-out-swinging-in-gameplay-trailer">Marvel’s Wolverine</a>, for its September&nbsp;15 launch. You can watch the latest trailer for that game <a href="https://gameinformer.com/state-of-play/2026/06/02/new-wolverine-gameplay-offers-first-look-at-jean-grey">here</a>.&nbsp;</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://gameinformer.com/2026/06/19/marvels-spider-man-2-is-getting-the-brand-new-day-suit]]></content:encoded>
